elerator seamlessly.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-empty-cloud-accelerator-manager\":\"Assign the first Cloud Accelerator manager to streamline team access to cloud data.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-empty-cloud-v2\":\"Assign the first accelerator manager to streamline team access to cloud data.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-empty-process-accelerator-manager\":\"Assign the first Process Accelerator manager so you can start creating repositories for your team.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-empty-process-v3\":\"Assign the first accelerator manager so you can start creating repositories for your team.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-title-accelerator-managers\":\"Existing {addon} Accelerator managers\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-existing-title-v3\":\"Existing accelerator managers\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-searcher-agility-empty-state\":\"This user doesn't exist on your account. To add yourself as an Agility Accelerator manager, enter your full email address.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-searcher-cloud-empty-state\":\"This user doesn't exist on your account. To add yourself as a Cloud Accelerator manager, enter your full email address.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-searcher-empty-state-v2\":\"This user doesn't exist on your account. To add yourself as an accelerator manager, enter your full email address.\",\"team-control-center-manage-addon-owners-searcher-process-empty-state\":\"This user doesn't exist on your account. To add yourself as a Process Accelerator manager, enter your full email address.\",\"team-control-center-teams-header-remove-team-agile-v2\":\"Remove from Agility Accelerator\",\"team-control-center-teams-header-remove-team-cloud\":\"Remove from Cloud Accelerator\",\"team-control-center-teams-search-default-agile-placeholder-v2\":\"Search Agility Accelerator teams\",\"team-control